message.content:
{
  "output": "@startuml
actor Player
participant GameSystem

note right of Player: Rule 1
Player -> GameSystem: Start game
GameSystem -> Player: Enter names
note right of GameSystem: Rule 17
alt Name is "Computer"
  GameSystem -> Player: "Name cannot be Computer"
  Player -> GameSystem: Enter valid name
end

GameSystem -> GameSystem: Initialize points to 0 for all players
note right of GameSystem: Rule 2
GameSystem -> GameSystem: Randomize player order
note right of GameSystem: Rule 16

loop 12 times
  Player -> GameSystem: Decide to skip turn?
  note right of Player: Rule 20
  alt Player skips turn
    GameSystem -> Player: Next player's turn
  else Player does not skip
    Player -> GameSystem: Throw dice
    note right of Player: Rule 4
    GameSystem -> GameSystem: Update points
    note right of GameSystem: Rule 5
    alt Dice count is 1
      Player -> GameSystem: Decide to re-roll?
      note right of Player: Rule 9
      alt Player re-rolls
        Player -> GameSystem: Throw dice again
        GameSystem -> GameSystem: Update points
      end
    else Dice count is 2
      GameSystem -> GameSystem: Triple dice count
      note right of GameSystem: Rule 14
    else Dice count is even but not 2
      GameSystem -> GameSystem: Halve dice count
      note right of GameSystem: Rule 14
    else Dice count is 5
      Player -> GameSystem: Throw dice again
      GameSystem -> GameSystem: Multiply both dice counts
      note right of GameSystem: Rule 18
    else Dice count is 6
      GameSystem -> GameSystem: Skip next player's turn
      note right of GameSystem: Rule 13
    end
    alt Points above 5
      GameSystem -> GameSystem: Change point color to yellow
      note right of GameSystem: Rule 19
    end
    alt Points above 11
      GameSystem -> GameSystem: Change point color to purple
      note right of GameSystem: Rule 12
    end
    alt Points are equal
      GameSystem -> GameSystem: Print "Equality!"
      note right of GameSystem: Rule 15
    end
    alt Same value three times in a row
      GameSystem -> GameSystem: Reset points to 0
      note right of GameSystem: Rule 21
    end
    GameSystem -> Player: Print dice count and points
    note right of GameSystem: Rule 6
  end
  alt One player has 10 more points than others
    GameSystem -> GameSystem: End game
    note right of GameSystem: Rule 8
  end
end

GameSystem -> GameSystem: Determine winner
note right of GameSystem: Rule 24
GameSystem -> Player: Print players' points and winner
note right of GameSystem: Rule 23
alt Players decide to play again
  GameSystem -> GameSystem: Order players by last game's points ascending
  note right of GameSystem: Rule 25
end

Player -> GameSystem: Winner receives message
note right of Player: Rule 10
@enduml"
}

{
  "output": "@startuml
actor Player
participant GameSystem

note right of Player: Rule 1
Player -> GameSystem: Start Game

note right of GameSystem: Rule 2
GameSystem -> Player: Initialize points to 0

note right of GameSystem: Rule 16
GameSystem -> Player: Decide turn order randomly

note right of GameSystem: Rule 17
Player -> GameSystem: Enter name
alt Name is "Computer"
  GameSystem -> Player: Print "Name cannot be Computer"
  Player -> GameSystem: Enter name again
end

loop 12 times
  note right of GameSystem: Rule 3
  GameSystem -> Player: It's your turn
  
  note right of Player: Rule 20
  Player -> GameSystem: Decide to skip turn
  alt Player skips turn
    GameSystem -> Player: Skip turn
  else
    note right of Player: Rule 4
    Player -> GameSystem: Throw dice
    
    note right of GameSystem: Rule 9
    alt Dice count is 1
      Player -> GameSystem: Decide to re-roll
      alt Player re-rolls
        Player -> GameSystem: Throw dice again
      end
    end
    
    note right of GameSystem: Rule 14
    alt Dice count is 2
      GameSystem -> GameSystem: Triple dice count
    else Dice count is even but not 2
      GameSystem -> GameSystem: Halve dice count
    end
    
    note right of GameSystem: Rule 18
    alt Dice count is 5
      Player -> GameSystem: Throw dice again
      GameSystem -> GameSystem: Multiply both dice counts
    end
    
    note right of GameSystem: Rule 5
    GameSystem -> Player: Add dice count to points
    
    note right of GameSystem: Rule 19
    alt Points > 5
      GameSystem -> Player: Change point color to yellow
    end
    
    note right of GameSystem: Rule 12
    alt Points > 11
      GameSystem -> Player: Change point color to purple
    end
    
    note right of GameSystem: Rule 21
    alt Same value thrown three times
      GameSystem -> Player: Reset points to 0
    end
    
    note right of GameSystem: Rule 6
    GameSystem -> Player: Print dice count and points
    
    note right of GameSystem: Rule 15
    alt Points are equal
      GameSystem -> Player: Print "Equality!"
    end
    
    note right of GameSystem: Rule 13
    alt Dice count is 6
      GameSystem -> Player: Skip next player's turn
    end
  end
end

note right of GameSystem: Rule 7
alt 12 turns completed
  note right of GameSystem: Rule 24
  GameSystem -> Player: Determine winner
  note right of GameSystem: Rule 10
  GameSystem -> Player: Print "Congratulations " + player name + " you won the game! You are the best!"
else Rule 8
  alt One player has 10 more points than others
    GameSystem -> Player: End game
  end
end

note right of GameSystem: Rule 23
GameSystem -> Player: Print players' points and winner

note right of GameSystem: Rule 25
alt Players decide to play again
  GameSystem -> Player: Order players by last game's points ascending
end
@enduml"
}

{
  "output": "@startuml
actor Player
participant GameSystem

note right of Player: Rule 1
Player -> GameSystem: Start Game

note right of GameSystem: Rule 2
GameSystem -> Player: Initialize points to 0

note right of GameSystem: Rule 16
GameSystem -> Player: Decide turn order

loop 12 turns
  note right of Player: Rule 3
  Player -> GameSystem: Take turn
  
  note right of Player: Rule 4
  Player -> GameSystem: Throw dice
  
  alt Dice count is 1
    note right of GameSystem: Rule 9
    GameSystem -> Player: Decide to re-roll
  end
  
  alt Dice count is 2
    note right of GameSystem: Rule 14
    GameSystem -> Player: Triple dice count
  else Dice count is even
    note right of GameSystem: Rule 14
    GameSystem -> Player: Halve dice count
  end
  
  alt Dice count is high
    note right of GameSystem: Rule 18
    GameSystem -> Player: Throw again and multiply
  end
  
  note right of GameSystem: Rule 5
  GameSystem -> Player: Add dice count to points
  
  note right of GameSystem: Rule 6
  GameSystem -> Player: Print dice count and points
  
  alt Player points > 5
    note right of GameSystem: Rule 19
    GameSystem -> Player: Change point color to purple
  end
  
  alt Player throws 6
    note right of GameSystem: Rule 13
    GameSystem -> Player: End turn
  end
  
  alt Player throws same value multiple times
    note right of GameSystem: Rule 21
    GameSystem -> Player: Reset points to 0
  end
  
  alt Players' points are equal
    note right of GameSystem: Rule 15
    GameSystem -> Player: Print "Equality!"
  end
  
  alt Player skips turn
    note right of Player: Rule 20
    Player -> GameSystem: Skip turn
  end
end

alt Game ends after 12 turns
  note right of GameSystem: Rule 7
  GameSystem -> Player: End game
else One player has significantly more points
  note right of GameSystem: Rule 8
  GameSystem -> Player: End game
end

alt Two players have the same points
  note right of GameSystem: Rule 22
  GameSystem -> Player: Continue game
end

note right of GameSystem: Rule 24
GameSystem -> Player: Declare winner

note right of GameSystem: Rule 10
GameSystem -> Player: Congratulate winner

alt Players decide to play again
  note right of GameSystem: Rule 25
  GameSystem -> Player: Order players in a certain way
end

note right of GameSystem: Rule 23
GameSystem -> Player: Print players' points and winner

@enduml"
}

{
  "output": "@startuml
actor Player
participant Game

Player -> Game: Start Game
note right of Game: Rule 1, 2, 16

loop 12 times
  Player -> Game: Take Turn
  note right of Game: Rule 3
  alt Player chooses to skip
    note right of Game: Rule 20
  else Player throws dice
    Player -> Game: Throw Dice
    note right of Game: Rule 4
    Game -> Player: Dice Count
    alt Dice Count is 1
      note right of Game: Rule 9
    else Dice Count is 2
      note right of Game: Rule 14
    else Dice Count is even
      note right of Game: Rule 14
    else Dice Count is high
      note right of Game: Rule 18
    end
    Game -> Player: Update Points
    note right of Game: Rule 5
    alt Dice Count is 6
      note right of Game: Rule 13
    end
    alt Player throws same value multiple times
      note right of Game: Rule 21
    end
    Game -> Player: Print Dice Count and Points
    note right of Game: Rule 6
    alt Points are equal
      Game -> Player: Print "Equality!"
      note right of Game: Rule 15
    end
    alt Player's points > 5
      note right of Game: Rule 19
    end
    alt Player's points are sufficient to win
      note right of Game: Rule 12
    end
  end
end

alt Game ends after 12 turns
  note right of Game: Rule 7
else One player has significantly more points
  note right of Game: Rule 8
end

alt Two players have the same points
  note right of Game: Rule 22
end

Game -> Player: Print Winner
note right of Game: Rule 10, 23, 24

alt Players decide to play again
  note right of Game: Rule 25
end

@enduml"
}
